Intel Smart Sound Technology (SST) Audio Driver for FreeBSD.

This driver supports Intel Broadwell-U/Haswell platforms (e.g., Dell XPS 13 9343)
providing support for the SST DSP and connected codecs (RT286/ALC3263) over I2S.
It replaces the standard HDA driver for audio playback and capture on these devices.

Features:
- Full DSP initialization and firmware loading
- PCM playback and recording via sound(4)
- Headphone/Mic jack detection
- Volume control and EQ preset support
